<html>
  <head>
    <title>Apply</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Apply Now!</h1>
    <p>All majors are accepted. Looking for students to fulfill positions in <b>accounting</b>, <b>finance/economics</b>, <b>human resources</b>, <b>marketing</b>, and <b>technology</b>.</p>
    <h3><u>Requirements to Join:</u></h3>
    <p>
      <ul>
        <li>Minimum 3.0 GPA</li>
        <li>An Attached Resume</li>
        <li>Knowledge/Interest in Investing</li>
        <li>Able to attend weekly meetings as well as mandatory events</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <form>
      <label>
        Name:
        <input type="text" name="name" required="required" />
      </label>
      <br />
      
      <label>
        Email:
        <input type="email" name="email" required="required" />
      </label>
      <br />
      
      <label>
        Major:
        <input type="text" name="major" required="required" />
      </label>
      <br />
      
      <p>
        <label for="background">
          Investing Background:
        </label>
        <br />
        <textarea>Enter your investing background...</textarea>
      </p>

      <p>
        Position Applying For:
        <br />
        <label>
          <input type="checkbox" name="position" value="accounting" />
          Accounting
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type="checkbox" name="position" value="finance/economics" />
          Finance/Economics
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type="checkbox" name="position" value="hr" />
          Human Resources/Alumni Relations
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type="checkbox" name="position" value="marketing" />
          Marketing
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type="checkbox" name="position" value="technology" />
          Technology
        </label>
      </p>

      <p>
        Grade Level:
        <br />
        <label>
          <input type="radio" name="grade" value="freshman" />
          Freshman
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type="radio" name="grade" value="sophomore" />
          Sophomore
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type="radio" name="grade" value="junior" />
          Junior
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type="radio" name="grade" value="senior" />
          Senior
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type="radio" name="grade" value="other" />
          Other
        </label>
      </p>

      <p>Upload Your Resume:</p>
      <input type="file" name="resume" /><br />
      <input type="submit" value="Upload" />

      <p>
        <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
      </p>
    </form
  </body>
</html>